# {{.Name}} CLI Skill

Use the `{{.Name}}` CLI to interact with the {{.Name}} API.

## Authentication

```bash
{{.Name}} auth login    # Interactive OAuth login
{{.Name}} auth status   # Check authentication status
```

## Common Commands

```bash
# List resources
{{.Name}} <resource> list

# Show details
{{.Name}} <resource> show <id>

# Create
{{.Name}} <resource> create --name "New Resource"
```

## Output Formats

- Default (TTY): Styled terminal output
- `--json`: Full JSON envelope
- `--quiet`: Raw JSON data only
- `--agent`: JSON + suppress prompts
- `--ids-only`: One ID per line
- `--count`: Integer count
